        "description": "The world needs your help after a lab experiment went wrong! Giant ants, a protist, and fungi are taking over the city! Humanity relies on you and your AI assistant STEVE to bring everything back to normal! Immerse yourself in the worlds within worlds that surround us every day, but usually go unnoticed by the human eye – all in the iconic kurzgesagt style. Throughout 4 missions, you’ll learn about the concept of scales and the different rules that apply to different size-based realms – from molecular and bacterial to the insect, human, and even mountain-sized world!\n\nBut wait, there’s more! Watch your favorite 2D Kurzgesagt videos in a whole new way with Duck and friends – in the kurzgesagt Multiplayer Theater. Or bring objects and creatures you collected in-game to life in your own home via the Mixed Reality Sandbox and immerse yourself even further into the colorful world of kurzgesagt. \n",
